        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix: hoist timer declaration to avoid TDZ ReferenceError in abortable delay",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\nFixes a latent TDZ bug where `finish()` references `timer` declared as `const` after `finish` was defined, risking `ReferenceError` if abort fires before timer assignment.\n\n## Why This Change Was Made\n\nHoist `timer` as `let` above `finish` so it is safely `undefined` when `finish` fires early.\n\n## User Impact\n\nNo user-visible change. Removes fragile declaration-order dependency.\n\n## Evidence\n\n```\nextensions/feishu/src/async.test.ts\nTest Files  1 passed (1)\n     Tests  5 passed (5)\n[test] passed 1 Vitest shard in 9.75s\n```",
